of the Windsor Park neighborhood; revising provisions governing
the use of certain money for the purposes of the Act; extending the
reversion date of appropriations made for the purposes of the Act;
making various other changes relating to housing; making [an
appropriation;] appropriations; and providing other matters properly
relating thereto.
